244
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:45,359
Kakak Xiu.

245
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:50,119
Lihat posisi tabung bambu ini, tetap kau.

246
00:17:52,799 --> 00:17:53,880
Kalau begitu, aku lanjut tanya satu lagi.

247
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:56,680
Apakah orang yang kau sukai ada di sini?

248
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,640
Lan, kurasa kau sengaja.

249
