00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:54,480
Pulang.

295
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,079
Pulang.

296
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:01,039
Setelah bangun, sudah bisa pulang.

297
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:08,319
Kau begitu ingin pulang?

298
00:21:08,384 --> 00:21:12,800
♪Kata-kata cinta melukiskan lingkaran♪

299
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,559
Ingin pulang.

300
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:25,280
